                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9697" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2427</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">657 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柚香柚美：度尾仙溪果业专业合作社绿色产业转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Pomelo&#39;s Fragrance and Beauty: The Green Industrial  Transformation Path of Duwei Xianxi Fruit Industry  Professional Cooperative</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马改艳，黄曦涛，吴林坤，辜文涛，王恒波，李树茂</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建省仙游县度尾镇仙溪果业合作社</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合作社；文旦柚；战略定位；可持续发展；产业绿色转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ooperative；Wendan pomelo；Strategic Positioning; Sustainable Development; Green Transformation of Industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">度尾文旦柚是莆田四大名果之一，拥有200余年的栽培历史，凭借优良品质与独特风味，蜚声海内外，成为仙游县经济发展的重要支柱产业。尽管文旦柚声名远扬，但面临农产品亟需解决的发展瓶颈。管理上缺乏统一标准、品牌化建设尚不成熟、土壤酸化问题突出、施肥方式不科学，裂果率居高不下等，这些局限性严重制约了产业的进一步发展。度尾仙溪果业专业合作社借助政策扶持的契机，积极探索推进文旦柚产业绿色发展，在竞争激烈的市场环境中脱颖而出，冲破困境。本案例通过讲述度尾文旦柚产业的发展历程，深入剖析合作社解决产业难题的举措，不仅有助于学生理解利益链接机制理论、企业社会责任理论、资源整合理论和供应链管理理论以及政策扶持在产业发展中的重要作用，还能激发学生对解决农业产业实际问题的思考与探索精神。同时，案例中展现的创新与奋进精神，也为培养具有时代使命感的农业领域人才提供了重要启示，助力推动农业产业的可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As one of the four famous fruits in Putian, Citrus maxima ‘duweiwendan’ is a unique and precious fruit in Duwei Town, Xianyou County, with a cultivation history of more than 200 years. With its excellent quality and unique flavor, it has become famous both at home and abroad. It has been selected as a geographical indication protected product in Xianyou and has become an important pillar industry for the economic development of Xianyou County. However, in recent years, although Wendan pomelo is well - known, it still faces common production bottlenecks of agricultural products. There is a lack of unified management standards, the brand-building is not yet mature, the problem of soil acidification is prominent, the fertilization method is unscientific, and the fruit-cracking rate remains high. These limitations seriously restrict the further development of the industry. In order to break through the existing difficulties in the Wendan pomelo industry, Duwei Xianxi Fruit Industry Professional Cooperative takes the opportunity of policy support, actively explores, promotes the green development of the Wendan pomelo industry, and strives to stand out in the highly competitive market environment. This case tells the development history of the Duwei Wendan pomelo industry and deeply analyzes the measures taken by the cooperative to solve industrial problems. This not only helps students understand the important roles of the Interest Linkage Mechanism Theory, Corporate Social Responsibility Theory, Resource Integration Theory, Supply Chain Management Theory, and policy support in industrial development, but also stimulates students&#39; thinking and exploration spirit in solving practical problems in the agricultural industry. At the same time, the innovative and enterprising spirit demonstrated in the case also provides important inspiration for cultivating agricultural talents with a sense of mission in the new era and helps to promote the sustainable development of the agricultural industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略定位；战略协同；战略差异化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
